Invocation Name: fun questions
des:
Ask for a fun question and see if that makes you laugh out loud!

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Fun Questions" or "Alexa, open Fun Questions" to get a question".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
